assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Munshaat Real Estate Projects Company K.S.C.P., together with its subsidiaries, owns, develops, sells, and purchases real estate properties in Kuwait and internationally. The company also operates, manages, rents, and invests in hotels, clubs, motels, entertainment houses, rest places, gardens, parks, exhibitions, restaurants, cafeterias, residential complexes, tourism and health products, recreational and sports projects, shops on various degrees and levels. In addition, it is involved in the provision of consultation services in various real estate fields; maintenance work for buildings and real estates, including maintenance, civil, mechanical and electrical, lift, and air conditioning works; real estate auctions; owning and managing of commercial markets and residential complexes; and developing and managing of real estate investment funds. The company was founded in 2003 and is based in Kuwait City, Kuwait. Munshaat Real Estate Projects Company K.S.C.P. is a subsidiary of Aref Investment Group S.A.K.
